description: A human resource office has information about all employees including: salary, marital status, age, etc. The task is to create a decision model that calculates minimal, maximal, and average salaries along with a number of high-paid employees using rules like 'Salary > 85000'. The data includes the following fields: Name, Marital Status, Gender, Age, and Salary. The model should also calculate the mean age of the employees and identify the employees who are low paid (salary <= 30000).
